WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.179
Successfully executing this joint motion requires you to intimately understand

00:00:04.179 --> 00:00:08.358
the internal roles within Amazon, as their financial targets vary

00:00:08.358 --> 00:00:12.537
dramatically. Account Managers are aggressively targeted to grow their assigned

00:00:12.537 --> 00:00:16.715
accounts' direct cloud spend and are highly motivated to push

00:00:16.715 --> 00:00:20.894
marketplace purchases, while Partner Sales Managers hold specific targets to

00:00:20.894 --> 00:00:25.073
grow the revenue allocated explicitly to partners like AppsFlyer. Meanwhile,

00:00:25.073 --> 00:00:29.252
Partner Development Managers are evaluated strictly on overarching partnership performance

00:00:29.252 --> 00:00:33.431
metrics, shared opportunity volume, and regional market expansion.
